description: The rescuer had an oxygen mask and descended with ropes to save the bird.
title: Rescuer abseils down well to save trapped owl
title_page: Rescuer abseils down well to save trapped owl - BBC News
maintext: They got to the bird just in time, as a probe lowered into the well indicated that there was little air inside. They used a powerful light and telescope to locate the owl, before sending a rescuer down with breathing apparatus.
